# Special Request Slack App

## Setup Instructions
1. Clone the repository
2. Run \`npm install\`
3. Create a .env file with required Slack tokens
4. Set up Slack App in Slack Developer Portal

## Environment Variables
- SLACK_BOT_TOKEN
- SLACK_SIGNING_SECRET
- SLACK_APP_TOKEN
- SPECIAL_REQUESTS_CHANNEL

## Development
